  <front>
   <head>IN IMITATION OF ANACREON.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="octet">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">'em Censure: what care I?</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">The Herd of Criticks I defie.</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Let the Wretches know, I write</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Regardless of their Grace, or Spight.</l>
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">No, no: the Fair, the Gay, the Young</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Govern the Numbers of my Song.</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">All that They approve is sweet:</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And All is Sense, that They repeat.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="octet">
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Bid the warbling Nine retire:</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">, String thy Servant's Lyre:</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Love shall be my endless Theme:</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Pleasure shall triumph over Fame:</l>
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And when these Maxims I decline,</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">, may Thy Fate be Mine:</l>
     <l n="15" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">May I grasp at empty Praise;</l>
     <l n="16" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">And lose the Nymph, to gain the Bays.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
